Pre-Game Insights: South Africa have a depleted squad with Quinton de Kock, David Miller, Kagiso Rabada, Lungi Ngidi and Anrich Nortje all leaving for IPL.
Adding more misery is an injury to Temba Bavuma. Reeza Hendricks has also withdrawn on paternity grounds.
Skipper Klassen has a tough task at hand.
For Pakistan, it is yet another chance to assert their authority and win their fifth series.
